metadataStandardName.gco:CharacterString: ISO 19139 Geographic Information - Metadata - Implementation Specification

abstract.gco:CharacterString: This Census block group data was retrieved from the U.S. Census data site. Data in each column represents population estimates from specified years. The population information in the 2010 column is the full summary population from the 2010 decennial census. Each year from 2013-2017 contains population estimates from the 5-year American Community Survey. Please refer to the Census website for more information. The data is a product of the United States Census and was not produced by Denton County, Texas.The data can be downloaded and joined to respective datasets using the GEOID fields.

purpose.gco:CharacterString: Census block group population data for Denton County merged from various datasets. Years: 2010 (full census), 2013-2017 (5-Year American Community Survey estimates). Full datasets can be found on the Census data site.

useLimitation.gco:CharacterString: This data is a product of the United States Census Bureau and solely used for the purposes of visualization and information-sharing by Denton County, Texas.
